text: Pogonocherus pesarinii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Sama in 1993. It is known from Morocco.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus pesarinii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1993
